# Home Dashboard rules

## Must
- Use `Grid container spacing={4}` for the dashboard section.
- Use MUI `Card` surfaces for panels.
- Use `List` + `ListItem` + `Avatar` for candidate/user rows.
- All copy must be Hebrew only.
- In dark mode, panel surfaces and section backgrounds must use warm brown layered tones from theme tokens.
- Preserve pink accent usage where relevant to maintain brand consistency.

## Never
- Do not embed layout-critical styles in CSS; use MUI `sx` + theme tokens.
- Do not use black/navy hardcoded dark backgrounds in dashboard sections.

